cowboy
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a (junior) stationhand who milks the house cow, and tends to domestic chores; now cowman(-gardener).
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:contrast cattle man
Pronunciation:
Notes:
